name: Unidentified_Narkina_5_intake_warden
content:
A human male intake warden was an Imperial officer serving as a prison guard in the Imperial Prison Complex in Narkina 5. As one of the highest ranking officers in the facility alongside the prison commander, he welcomed newcomers and demonstrated the prison's unique discipline method: its signature shock-inducing Tunqstoid steel floors. During the Uprising on Narkina 5 he and many other prison wardens locked themselves in a storage cupboard to hide from the escaped inmates.
The intake warden appeared in the eighth episode of the first season of the live-action series Andor, "Narkina 5." He was played by Paul McEwan.
